metadata.description:
This artwork may or may not be for the love of peach (it is).  
 
Inspired by the explosion of fun permissionless derivatives that have followed the incredible Visualize Value edition, Checks.

The original VV piece can be found here: https://create.zora.co/collections/0x34eebee6942d8def3c125458d1a86e0a897fd6f9

Breakdown of the thought process behind the original can be found here:  
https://twitter.com/jackbutcher/status/1611726527590187016
